#Python price tracker
A Python script that scrapes a products price and creates CSV file 
## Functionality
- Scrapes the products live price using the libraries beautifulsoup and requests
- Saves the price and the timestamp within a CSV file
- Alerts when product price drops
##Libraries used
- requests
- beautifulsoup4
- CSV
- Daytime
## How to run tool 
1. Install dependencies
pip install beautifulsoup4 request
2. Run the Scripts
python price-tracker.py
## Use swap the URL with the product page URL to set product price thresholds
